    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>We tested pre-pandemic (2015-2019) plasma samples from 148 Vietnamese children, and 100 Vietnamese adults at high risk of zoonotic infections, for antibodies against SARS-CoV-2 nucleocapsid and spike proteins. None was positive, indicating no prior serological cross-reactivity with SARS-CoV-2 that might explain the low numbers of COVID-19 in Vietnam.</jats:p>",
    "DOI": "10.1101/2021.07.12.21260379",
